  comment "Objective:
========
* Introduce a smart material class, which is able to represent general materials in a general and consistent manner
* Ability to rotate material matrices
* Ability to calculate matrices for plane-stree, plane-strain etc.
* Ability to include arbitrary non-linear dependencies, e.g. temperature, b-h-curve, frequency dependence, stress-strain-relationship, damping-behaviour etc.
* Additionally a new file-representation of the material class should be established, which is bases on a xml-file structure

Affected Classes:
==============
* MaterialData
* LoadMaterialData*
* All classes, which use Material (Forms, PDEs)
* XML-Writer class (i.e. XMLParamHandler)"
